      "to_id": "cec50b17:0",
      "content": "DONE — delegate_task and report_done MCP tools implemented. Build clean (tsc, no errors).\n\n**Files changed (5):**\n- `src/db.ts` (+13/-2): `sendMessage` now returns `number` (lastInsertRowid). Added `getMostRecentInProgressActivity(agentId)` helper that returns `{ id }` or null.\n- `src/mcp-server.ts` (+66/-1): Added import for `getMostRecentInProgressActivity`. Added `delegate_task` and `report_done` tool definitions. Added both handlers (before throw).\n- `templates/SYNAPSE.md` (+2): Added `delegate_task` and `report_done` rows to the MCP tools table.\n- `templates/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md` (+7/-5): \"Recording task activities\" rewritten — steps 1+2 collapsed into `delegate_task`, step 5 added for PLAN.md update.\n- `templates/SYNAPSE-worker.md` (+2/-3): Per-task workflow steps 3+4 collapsed into `report_done`.\n\n**Existing tools:** `send_message`, `start_activity`, `finish_activity` are all still present and unchanged — backward compat preserved.\n\n**Activity lookup:** factored into `getMostRecentInProgressActivity` in db.ts — cleaner than inline SQL in the handler.\n\n**Lifecycle traces:**\n1. delegate_task → message inserted → activity inserted with agent_id=to_id, trigger_msg_id=message_id → returns both ids. ✓\n2. report_done → full message to orchestrator → milestone to human → getMostRecentInProgressActivity finds the row → finishActivity sets status=completed, result_msg_id=orchMsgId. ✓\n3. Combined: delegate_task → worker report_done → activity has trigger_msg_id + result_msg_id + status=completed → orchestrator commits → commit hook adds commit_sha (row already completed, COALESCE guard preserved). ✓\n\nNot committed per instructions.",
